{"tid":896546,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線]俾1800萬你你會用黎做咩？","createTime":"2018-11-10T06:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:42:44.000Z","uid":122438,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c6b1baa3919161376e360181a8da95f02b872e","tid":896546,"uid":122438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"租百萬呎園林 十數年不干預  最奢侈生態實驗<br />\n<br />\n這片地的主人是兩父子：父親韋尉，和兒子韋翃箖。韋尉今年56歲，從事園林生態30多年了。這片園子是16年前租下來的，租期22年。<br />\n韋尉不喜歡人工干預園林生態，而深信，要改變環境，必須建立持久的生態循環，這片地，就是他的一種烏托邦試驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/248545/最強環保l-租百萬呎園林-十數年不干預-最奢侈生態實驗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2F248545%2F%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9Dl-%E7%A7%9F%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%91%8E%E5%9C%92%E6%9E%97-%E5%8D%81%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90-%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%A2%E4%BE%88%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97&d=lmhI%2F5UZH7%2FTQnJvND34gE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=0eecd65e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/248545/最強環保l-租百萬呎園林-十數年不干預-最奢侈生態實驗</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在，園子也對外開放，但父子倆還是希望來的人越少越好，一次接待不能超過35人，因為人一多，鳥就會飛散而去。他們甚至計畫在園子裡搭建一個觀鳥隧道，人在下面走，鳥在外面歇息，對於他們來說，需要被束縛的不應該是動物，而是人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/144207_4728316951be40078ddb325d04968c23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F144207_4728316951be40078ddb325d04968c23.jpg&h=4e0df5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/144209_67937f3f45962cc7fd35d6d33b58a511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F144209_67937f3f45962cc7fd35d6d33b58a511.jpg&h=706a62c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/144210_1fe7f5d598666f053b73b372816aa500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim